text: Raghd Magdy (born 7 March 1983) is an Egyptian table tennis player, born in Iraq. She competed in women's team at the 2012 Summer Olympics in London. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian female table tennis players Category:Olympic table tennis players of Egypt Category:Table tennis players at the 2012 Summer Olympics
